benchmark_config.jira_title: Implement/Test API: PUT /1.0/kb/bundles/{bundleId}/renameKey - Update a bundle externalKey

covered: Valid Request: Scenario TC01 covers successful update with correct headers and body.
Error handling for missing required header: TC02.
Additional headers X-Killbill-Reason and X-Killbill-Comment: TC14.
Regression test for problematic externalKey: TC18.
gaps: Limited coverage of system limits on externalKey length (e.g., maximum allowed length not explicitly tested).
No explicit tests for rate limiting or throttling behavior.
No tests for caching headers or cache validation mechanisms.
No explicit concurrency conflict resolution scenarios beyond basic concurrent requests.
No tests for detailed validation of externalKey character set restrictions (e.g., allowed/disallowed characters).
recommendations: Add explicit tests for maximum externalKey length limits and validation of character set restrictions.
Include rate limiting and throttling tests to verify system stability under high request volume.
Implement tests to verify caching headers like ETag and Cache-Control for idempotency and cache validation.
Enhance concurrency testing to simulate race conditions and conflict resolution strategies.
Add detailed validation tests for externalKey character restrictions and trimming rules.
